the Book (ie. the Holy Qur’an) as exactly as it should be recited, strove for the sake of Allah as exactly as striving must be, and faced all troubles steadfastly for His sake, seeking his reward, until death came upon you.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ASH-HADO ANNAKA QAD AQAMTAS SALAATA WA AATAYTAZ ZAKAATA WA AMARTA BIL MA’ROOFE WA NAHAYTA A’NIL MUNKARE WA TALAWTAL KETAABA HAQQA TELAAWATEHI WA JAAHAD-TA FILLAAHE HAQQA JEHAADEHI WA SABARTA A’LAL AZAA FEE JAMBEHI MOHTASEBAN HATTAA ATAAKAL YAQEEN.", "ArabicText1": "اَشْہَدُ اَنَّکَ قَدْ اَقَمْتَ الصَّلٰوۃَ وَاٰتَیْتَ الزَّکٰوۃَ وَاَمَرْتَ بِالْمَعْرُوْفِ وَنَہَیْتَ عَنِ الْمُنْکَرِ وَتَلَوْتَ الْکِتَابَ حَقَّ تِلَاوَتِہٖ وَجَاہَدْتَ فِیْ اللہِ حَقَّ جِہَادِہٖ وَصَبَرْتَ عَلَی الْاَذٰی فِیْ جَنْبِہٖ مُحْتَبِسًا حَتّٰی اَتٰیکَ الْیَقِیْنُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "Arabic